[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0714","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0714.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0459","title":"Linux Alpha MILO 本地拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Alpha Linux 系统中存在本地拒绝服务漏洞。本地攻击者可通过 MILO 引导加载程序强制系统重新启动，导致系统服务不可用。该漏洞影响运行 Alpha Linux 的 DEC Alpha 架构系统，攻击者需具备本地访问权限，无需高权限即可利用，CVSS 评分 4.6，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0459"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-02-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:26.440","remediation":"建议升级 MILO 引导程序至最新版本，并限制系统本地用户的登录访问权限。在生产环境中应禁用不必要的本地用户账号，并通过 `/etc/security/access.conf` 或 PAM 模块限制控制台访问。对于 Alpha 架构系统，可考虑迁移至更新的 Linux 内核版本以规避该引导层问题。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0459"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0714.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0644","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0644.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0403","title":"Cyrix CPU Linux 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Cyrix CPU 在 Linux 系统中存在硬件设计缺陷，本地攻击者可通过执行特定指令序列触发处理器异常，导致系统崩溃或拒绝服务。该漏洞影响使用 Cyrix 处理器的 Linux 系统，攻击者需拥有本地用户权限才能利用，无法远程触发。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0403"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-02-01","updated":"1999-02-01","remediation":"更换非 Cyrix 品牌的处理器，或升级 Linux 内核至包含 Cyrix CPU 异常处理补丁的版本。由于该漏洞为硬件设计缺陷，最彻底的修复方式是更换为 Intel 或 AMD 等主流处理器。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=91821080015725&w=2"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0644.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0591","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0591.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0360","title":"Microsoft Site Server 2.0 任意文件上传漏洞","description":"Microsoft Site Server 2.0 与 IIS 4.0 存在任意文件上传漏洞，远程攻击者可通过 HTTP 协议向目标网站上传包含 ASP 脚本的恶意文件，从而在服务器端执行任意命令。该漏洞影响 Microsoft Site Server 2.0 及 IIS 4.0 版本，攻击者无需身份认证即可利用，危害等级高。厂商已发布安全更新修复此漏洞。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0360"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-01-30","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"安装 Microsoft 官方针对 Site Server 2.0 的安全更新补丁，或禁用 IIS 4.0 中 Site Server 上传目录的脚本执行权限（移除 Scripts 和 Execute 权限），限制匿名用户对上传目录的写入权限。由于该产品已停止支持，建议迁移至受支持的替代产品。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=91763097004101&w=2"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0591.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0717","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0717.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0461","title":"Linux rpcbind 远程源地址欺骗漏洞","description":"rpcbind（端口映射服务）存在认证缺陷漏洞，远程攻击者可通过伪造源地址向目标系统的 rpcbind 服务发送恶意请求，从而插入或删除 RPC 服务注册条目，破坏服务映射表或劫持 RPC 服务通信。该漏洞影响 Linux、IRIX 及 Wietse Venema 实现的 rpcbind 等多个版本，攻击者无需身份认证即可远程利用，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0461"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-01-28","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"升级 rpcbind 至已修复版本以解决源地址欺骗漏洞。在防火墙层面限制对 UDP/TCP 111 端口的访问，仅允许可信来源 IP 连接。配置 TCP Wrappers（/etc/hosts.allow 和 /etc/hosts.deny）限制 rpcbind 的访问来源。如非必要，可在服务配置中禁用 rpcbind 服务。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0461","https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-1999-0461"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0717.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0571","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0571.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0348","title":"Microsoft IIS ASP 缓存信息泄露漏洞","description":"Microsoft Internet Information Server (IIS) 的 ASP 缓存机制存在信息泄露漏洞。当两个虚拟服务器共享同一物理目录时，ASP 脚本缓存未能正确隔离不同虚拟服务器之间的数据，导致攻击者可通过向目标服务器发送特制请求，获取同一物理目录下其他虚拟站点的敏感信息。该漏洞影响多个 IIS 版本，公开利用难度较低，可能导致网站配置文件、源代码等敏感数据泄露，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0348"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-01-27T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:12.237","remediation":"建议立即安装 Microsoft KB Q197003 安全更新（包含于 Windows NT 4.0 Security Rollup Package），该更新修复了 ASP 脚本缓存在虚拟服务器间的隔离问题。如无法安装补丁，应将每个虚拟服务器配置为使用独立的物理目录，避免不同虚拟主机共用同一目录；也可在 IIS 管理控制台中禁用 ASP 脚本文件缓存作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/default.aspx?scid=kb%3B%5BLN%5D%3BQ197003","http://www.osvdb.org/930","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ead50dc12e50bdd7f50b53d9d01c9f9946862c44/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0348.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0348","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0348.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/4ed191c1149de50e461e9a357f4a3a22e603f0d1/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0348.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/b7a93df7f7051799495805bc211adea8d202dae7/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-q6hg-qxrw-r3f8/GHSA-q6hg-qxrw-r3f8.json","https://github.com/marcellodesales/aibbp-reverse-engineer/blob/960f610d597aae9fec1cc5f03c68679be00c222d/reverse_engineer/invicti/vulnerabilities/db/vulnerabilities/vdb/1999/0xxx/cve-1999-0348.yaml","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0348.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153100_153200.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0571.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0573","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0573.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0349","title":"Microsoft IIS FTP LIST 命令缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Microsoft IIS 的 FTP 服务中的 list (ls) 命令存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可向目标服务器发送特制的 FTP 列表请求触发该漏洞，导致拒绝服务或远程代码执行。该漏洞影响早期版本的 IIS，攻击条件低，危害严重，建议及时安装安全补丁。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0349"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-01-27T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:12.357","remediation":"建议立即安装 Microsoft 安全公告 MS99-003 提供的补丁（Q223783），或升级至 IIS 5.0 及以上版本。如无法升级，可在 IIS 管理器中禁用 FTP 服务（停止 MSFTPSVC 服务），或限制匿名用户对 FTP 根目录的写入权限以降低风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/default.aspx?scid=kb%3B%5BLN%5D%3BQ188348","http://www.eeye.com/html/Research/Advisories/IIS%20Remote%20FTP%20Exploit/DoS%20Attack.html","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1999/ms99-003","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ead50dc12e50bdd7f50b53d9d01c9f9946862c44/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0349.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0349","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0349.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/4ed191c1149de50e461e9a357f4a3a22e603f0d1/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0349.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/b7a93df7f7051799495805bc211adea8d202dae7/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-hcx3-7fvg-jr7j/GHSA-hcx3-7fvg-jr7j.json","https://github.com/marcellodesales/aibbp-reverse-engineer/blob/960f610d597aae9fec1cc5f03c68679be00c222d/reverse_engineer/invicti/vulnerabilities/db/vulnerabilities/vdb/1999/0xxx/cve-1999-0349.yaml","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/I/iis_ftp_crash.nasl","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0349.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153100_153200.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0573.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0640","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0640.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0400","title":"Linux Kernel 2.2 ldd命令处理core文件拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Linux Kernel 2.2 版本的 ldd 命令在处理恶意构造的 core 文件时存在拒绝服务漏洞。本地攻击者可通过诱导用户在包含畸形数据的 core 文件上执行 ldd 命令，触发内核异常导致系统强制重启。该漏洞影响 Linux Kernel 2.2.0 及之前版本，CVSS 评分 4.6，危害等级中危。受影响的系统在攻击者获得普通用户权限后即可实施该攻击，无需额外认证。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0400"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1999-01-26T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:19.000","remediation":"升级 Linux 内核至 2.2.1 或更高版本，该版本已修复 ldd 解析 core 文件时的崩溃问题。如无法立即升级，作为临时缓解措施，禁止对不可信的 core 文件运行 ldd 命令，并通过 sysctl -w kernel.core_uses_pid=1 和设置 fs.suid_dumpable=0 限制核心转储文件的生成与访问权限。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/344","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19272","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/f4ffb7bcd93209aa53a757a7ebdf17fe2a18eb33/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0400.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0400","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0400.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a75ebb477762f54f32c38d85ec939339ec2712e5/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0400.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/e434c1da6464de3012c6c1eff8c0e19ef9669023/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-2x32-727m-44f2/GHSA-2x32-727m-44f2.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0400.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x1000/344/info.html","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_3.list.dict","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--e45afe65-1461-434d-a73e-c70299fe4ea0.json","https://github.com/shamedgh/confine/blob/a75dad3ad336e6258a42cd1ce4af061eea68ed76/cve.files/cveToFile.json.type.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0640.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0685","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0685.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0449","title":"Microsoft IIS 4 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Microsoft IIS 4.0 的 ExAir 示例站点中存在拒绝服务漏洞。远程攻击者无需身份认证，通过直接向 advsearch.asp、query.asp 或 search.asp 脚本发送特制请求，即可触发 CPU 资源耗尽，导致目标系统拒绝服务。该漏洞影响运行 IIS 4.0 的 Windows NT 4.0 系统，攻击条件低，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.8,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0449"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-01-26T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:25.213","remediation":"升级到 Windows 2000 及以上版本自带的 IIS 5.0 或更高版本，或直接移除 IIS 4 默认安装的 ExAir 示例站点目录（通常位于 C:\\InetPub\\iissamples\\exair），删除 advsearch.asp、query.asp、search.asp 等脚本文件。如无法升级，可在 IIS 管理器中禁用该示例站点的匿名访问权限作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.osvdb.org/2","http://www.osvdb.org/3","http://www.osvdb.org/4","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/193","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/6e5939e8074723d33adaf5b2f8b0352edab9ba8d/1999/CVE-1999-0449.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/727cf5277c8c23eaf8725829e26aff2ea619a86c/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0449.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0449","https://github.com/edoardottt/missing-cve-nuclei-templates/blob/36c16d53eb6071e39cfc3cf88e99f1b340ec913b/data/year/1999.txt","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/77fd3cf167afc5c82646a191836bcd2f9e51b459/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0449.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0449.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/18de81c56daca1c9e33223f0b95bdb8312a1ca75/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-9mvc-88j3-6fmc/GHSA-9mvc-88j3-6fmc.json","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/snort/drop-rules/web-iis.rules","https://github.com/marcellodesales/aibbp-reverse-engineer/blob/960f610d597aae9fec1cc5f03c68679be00c222d/reverse_engineer/invicti/vulnerabilities/db/vulnerabilities/vdb/1999/0xxx/cve-1999-0449.yaml","https://github.com/ivanitlearning/CTF-Repos/blob/b5364388a861fc7457409d494a9d075d73e7867e/Vulnhub/SkyTower/Web-scan.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0685.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0569","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0569.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0347","title":"Microsoft Internet Explorer 跨框架访问安全限制绕过漏洞","description":"Microsoft Internet Explorer 4.01 及 5.0.1 版本存在跨帧访问安全漏洞。远程攻击者可通过在 'about:' JavaScript URL 中插入 '%01' 特殊字符，诱使浏览器使用该字符后指定的域名解析页面，从而绕过同源策略限制，实现跨域读取本地文件内容或伪造任意网页。攻击者需诱导用户访问恶意构造的链接即可触发，无需任何身份认证，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0347"],"sources":["cve","exploitdb"],"published":"1999-01-26","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"升级到 Internet Explorer 5.5 及以上版本即可修复此漏洞。由于 Internet Explorer 已停止安全支持，强烈建议迁移到 Microsoft Edge 或其他现代浏览器（如 Chrome/Firefox），并启用 Windows 自动更新以保持系统安全。如无法升级浏览器，可在 IE 安全设置中将 Internet 区域安全级别设为高并禁用活动脚本。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=91745430007021&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=ntbugtraq&m=91756771207719&w=2"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0569.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0569.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0569.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0688","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0688.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0450","title":"Microsoft IIS 5.0 IISAPI扩展目录枚举漏洞","description":"Microsoft IIS 5.0 存在路径信息泄露漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向服务器发送特制的非存在 URL 请求（由 Perl 解释器 perl.exe 处理），从而枚举出 Web 服务器的真实物理路径。该漏洞影响 IIS 5.0 版本，攻击者无需身份认证即可利用，可能导致敏感系统路径信息泄露，为进一步攻击提供线索。CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0450"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-01-26","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"升级到受支持的 Windows Server 版本（IIS 5.0 已停止支持），或迁移至 IIS 7.0 及以上版本。如无法升级，在 IIS 管理器中删除 Perl ISAPI 扩展映射（perl.exe），并配置自定义错误页面禁止返回详细路径信息，同时限制 IIS 对非可执行目录的脚本映射权限。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/194","https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-1999-0450"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0688.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0688.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0688.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0584","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0584.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0352","title":"ControlIT（又名 Remotely Possible）弱密码加密漏洞","description":"ControlIT 4.5 及更早版本（又名 Remotely Possible）存在弱密码加密漏洞，其加密算法强度不足，导致存储在系统配置中的凭据可被轻易破解。远程攻击者若能够访问受影响系统的配置文件或通过网络嗅探获取加密后的密码，可通过逆向分析加密算法还原明文凭据，进而获取系统控制权。该漏洞影响 ControlIT 4.5 及更早版本，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0352"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-25T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:12.740","remediation":"建议立即升级 ControlIT 至 4.5 以上版本（若厂商已停止支持，应迁移至 Symantec pcAnywhere 或当前仍在维护的远程控制方案）。同时启用强密码策略，避免使用短于 8 位的密码，并限制远程访问来源 IP 以减少爆破风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0352"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0584.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0589","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0589.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0357","title":"Microsoft Windows 98 畸形 oshare 数据包远程拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Microsoft Windows 98 等操作系统在处理特制的 \"oshare\" 数据包时存在缺陷，远程攻击者可通过向目标系统发送包含无效分片偏移量的恶意网络数据包，触发系统资源耗尽或崩溃，导致拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 Windows 98 及可能存在类似问题的其他操作系统版本，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0357"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-01-25T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:13.350","remediation":"Windows 98 已终止支持，无官方补丁。建议在网络边界防火墙或路由器上过滤入站异常分片报文（drop invalid fragments），阻止恶意「oshare」数据包到达目标主机。若业务允许，应尽快升级至仍受支持的 Windows 版本（如 Windows 10/11）并安装最新安全更新。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0357","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ead50dc12e50bdd7f50b53d9d01c9f9946862c44/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0357.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0357","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0357.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/4ed191c1149de50e461e9a357f4a3a22e603f0d1/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0357.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/b7a93df7f7051799495805bc211adea8d202dae7/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-3x5w-w876-g26g/GHSA-3x5w-w876-g26g.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0357.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153100_153200.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0589.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0588","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0588.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0356","title":"CA ControlIT 地址簿用户凭证弱加密存储漏洞","description":"ControlIT v4.5及更早版本使用弱加密算法存储地址簿中的用户名和密码，攻击者可通过获取本地文件访问权限或网络嗅探等手段获取明文凭据，进而以合法用户身份登录系统实施进一步攻击。该漏洞影响所有运行ControlIT v4.5及更早版本的Windows平台，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可利用此漏洞获取系统控制权限。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0356"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-01-25","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"该产品已停止维护，无官方补丁可用。建议迁移至支持强加密（如AES-256）的远程控制方案。临时缓解措施包括：使用操作系统ACL限制地址簿文件仅允许管理员读取；避免在地址簿中存储明文凭据；在网络层面限制对ControlIT服务的访问。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0356"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0588.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0267","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0267.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0121","title":"CDE dtaction 缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"dtaction 是 CDE（通用桌面环境）工具集中的命令执行组件，其存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。本地攻击者可通过向 dtaction 提交超长参数触发缓冲区溢出，从而以 root 权限执行任意代码。该漏洞影响运行 CDE 的多款 Unix 系统（包括 Solaris、HP-UX、AIX 等），CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。厂商已发布补丁修复此问题。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0121"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-21T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:38.013","remediation":"立即移除 dtaction 二进制文件的 setuid root 权限：`chmod 0555 /usr/dt/bin/dtaction`，阻断本地普通用户以 root 权限执行。若业务允许，建议禁用 CDE 桌面环境（`/etc/init.d/dtlogin stop && chkconfig dtlogin off` 或相应平台等价操作）。各 Unix 厂商补丁：Solaris 安装 Sun Security Bulletin #00192 对应补丁 (patch ID 107021-01+)；HP-UX 安装 HPSBUX9909-103 对应补丁；AIX 安装 APAR IY08886 补丁；IRIX 升级至 6.5.15 或更高版本。同时限制可登录系统的本地用户范围，防止非受信用户获得交互式 shell 访问。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0121"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0267.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0265","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0265.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0119","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 4.0 共享资源未授权访问漏洞","description":"Windows NT 4.0 beta 版本存在权限验证缺陷，由于系统对共享资源的访问控制机制不完善，任意用户无需身份认证即可读取或删除网络共享目录中的文件。该漏洞影响 Windows NT 4.0 beta 测试版系统，攻击者可通过 SMB 协议远程访问目标主机上的共享资源，导致敏感信息泄露或数据丢失，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0119"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-01-19T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:37.760","remediation":"立即升级 Windows NT 4.0 beta 至 Windows NT 4.0 RTM 正式版，并安装最新 Service Pack 6a。为所有共享目录设置明确的 ACL 权限，禁止 Everyone 组具有读写权限，将共享目录所在分区转换为 NTFS 文件系统以启用更细粒度的访问控制，同时在注册表中将 RestrictAnonymous 键值设置为 1 以限制匿名访问。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/11"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0265.toml"}]